            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I think the larger question is can you (according to the spec) dynamically register an off-spec capability?\n\nMy gut says no, although @MariaSolOs might think differently?\n\nThe spec says\n```\nNot all clients need to support dynamic capability registration. A client opts in via the dynamicRegistration property on the specific client capabilities.\n```\nBut for a off-spec method, there is no dynamicRegistration property as there is no client capability for an off-spec method\n\n",
