            "body": "@tris203 I actually think that the spec is compatible with custom methods being dynamically registered. [Registrations](https://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol/specifications/lsp/3.17/specification/#registration) are typed quite vaguely, and I can think of several use cases where this might be desired. ",
